<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/alan-campbell> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Sir Alan Campbell was appointed Lord President of the Council, and Leader of the House of Commons on 5 September 2025. He was previously Parliamentary Secretary to the Treasury (Chief Whip) between 5 July 2024 and 5 September 2025. He was elected as the MP for Tynemouth in May 1997."@en .
